<font size=2>
This is 1st sub quest to SK Epic: <br> <br>This quest is part of the Shadowknight Epic Quest.  <br> <br>An ogre NPC named Smaka in the Neriak Foreign Quarter can make special cures. One of these includes a bottle of cough elixir which is required in the SK Epic Quest. For a mere 1000pp he will create you some cough elixir.  <br> <br>Smaka may also be part of other subquests but none are known at this time. <br>
