<font size=2>
This is 2nd sub quest to the epic: <br> <br>Decrepit Sheath <br> &nbsp; <br>  <br>This quest is part of the Shadowknight Epic Quest.  <br> <br>This sub-quest beings at an NPC named Teydar in the Qeynos Sewers. He spawns in the middle of the Blood Sabers lair so this may require some faction raising by ogres or trolls in order to not be killed on sight here.  <br> <br>Teydar can create you a decrepit sheath but he requires a few items. <br> <br>1) Decrepit Hide(These can be found off Ashenbone Drakes in the Plane of Hate). <br>2) Drake Spine(This can be found on a level 55 rare spawn drake named Rharzar in Rathe Mountains) <br>3) Enchanted Platinum Bar <br> <br>Returning him these items will result in a decrepit sheath.  <br>  <br>  <br>
